The '''2020 season''' was the '''[[Castleford Tigers]]'''' 95th season in the [[Rugby Football League]] and their 13th consecutive season in the top flight of [[Rugby league in England|English rugby league]]. The club competed in the [[2020 Super League season|2020 Super League]] and the [[2020 Challenge Cup]].

